HEADWORD: Thoroughstitch
<hw>Thor"ough*stitch`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>So as to
go the whole length of any business; fully; completely.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Preservance alone can carry us <qex>thoroughstitch</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

